exceptions.exn: In environment T : lattice f : T -> T x : T H : f x = x The term "T" has type "lattice" while it is expected to have type "?x <== ?y".

In environment H0 : forall (T : poset) (y x z : T), x <== y -> y <== z -> x <== z T : lattice f : T -> T x : T H : f x = x Unable to unify "?M1689 (tarski_lfp ?M1689) = tarski_lfp ?M1689" with "(let (mx_leq, _, _, _) := Poset.mixin (Poset.class T) in mx_leq) (tarski_lfp f) x".

original: intros x H. apply (poset_trans T _ _ _ H). apply tarski_lfp_fixed.
